.sin-max-width-container.mdl-grid.sin-how-it-works.sin-half-screen-vh
  .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
    .sin-icon__transformation-landing
    h3 Transform your data
    p Interactively build, modify and share data transformations. Transform data into RDF knowledge graphs. Reuse transformations to repeatably clean and transform data.
    = image_tag(image_url("screenshots/Grafterizer1.png"), id: 'show-ovl1')
  .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
    .sin-icon__hosting-landing
    h3 Host your data
    p Host and share your data on our reliable, cloud-based triple store (available for free to all users). Share data privately or publicly with other users of the platform.
    = image_tag(image_url("screenshots/Sparql1.png"), id: 'show-ovl2')
  .mdl-cell.mdl-cell--4-col
    .sin-icon__access-landing
    h3 Access your data
    p Visually explore data. Query data stored in your own SPARQL endpoint. Share and reuse SPARQL queries or use our APIs to access your data programatically.
    = image_tag(image_url("screenshots/Sparql4.png"), id: 'show-ovl3')
